Lay each piece of Parma ham on a board, cut off any surplus fat and discard.Spread a good teaspoon of goatsâ€™ cheese over the end quarter.  Season with salt and pepper.  Take a small handful of rocket and lay on top, leaving some of the rocket sticking out of the ends.  Lay one piece of cucumber on top.Roll the Parma ham up into a cigar shape and transfer to the fridge until needed.Slice each roll in half and arrange standing up on the cut side on a serving platter. Serve cold.